---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Company Profile | SEONGSANLAB Co., Ltd." 
	description="SEONGSANLAB Co., Ltd. is a technology-driven leader dedicated to industrial safety, integrating advanced ultrasonic Non-Destructive Testing (NDT) hardware with intelligent software systems." 
	lang="en"
>
	<!-- Company Vision Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative py-28 bg-[#0C1929] text-white overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-800">
		<!-- Dynamic Backlight Source -->
		<div class="absolute -top-40 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-cyan/20 to-transparent rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-blue-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
		
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
			<span class="inline-flex items-center space-x-1 text-sm font-sans bg-primary-cyan/10 text-primary-cyan border border-primary-cyan/20 px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
				About SEONGSANLAB
			</span>
			<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight font-display text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
				Measuring Safety, Ensuring Integrity:<br/>
				<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-cyan to-blue-400">Engineering the Future</span> of NDT Technology
			</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				Established in 2011, SEONGSANLAB Co., Ltd. is built on the belief that persistent R&D is the lifeblood of innovation, <br/>
				internalizing our entire product cycle—from circuit design to advanced medical & industrial ultrasonic solutions.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Company Message & Technical Philosophy -->
	<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white relative">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
			<div class="space-y-12">
				<div class="space-y-4 text-center">
					<span class="text-sm font-sans text-primary-cyan font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">Message & Philosophy</span>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white font-display">
						From Core Hardware to Intelligent Software:<br/>Leading the Localization & Evolution of Ultrasonic NDT
					</h2>
				</div>
				
				<div class="text-slate-300 text-sm sm:text-base space-y-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					<p>
						Dear Partners and Valued Clients,
					</p>
					<p>
						Welcome to SEONGSANLAB Co., Ltd. Since our incorporation in 2011, we have driven ultrasonic research with the unwavering belief that <strong>"Relentless Research and Development (R&D) is the lifeblood of industrial safety."</strong> In the domestic and international non-destructive testing (NDT) market, where advanced systems were heavily import-dependent, we successfully integrated medical ultrasound precision with robust industrial controls. Today, we internalize the entire product cycle—from circuit schematic board design and embedded firmware to real-time signal processing and desktop analytical suites.
					</p>
					<p>
						Our proprietary NDT brand <strong class="text-primary-cyan">DSPAUT</strong> and unified <strong class="text-primary-cyan">DSVision / DSViewer</strong> software platforms are engineered from severe inspection field insights. They deliver near-instantaneous operating speeds, highly intuitive controls, and field-tested structural durability that dramatically enhance operational efficiency.
					</p>
					<p>
						Moving forward, SEONGSANLAB aims to be more than a equipment supplier. By providing our open-API Software Development Kit (DSK), we actively share high-precision data access with domestic/international research institutions, aerospace agencies, and automation innovators. Backed by proprietary core technologies and official certifications, we promise to remain your most reliable engineering partner.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Premium Milestone Timeline (연혁) -->
	<section class="py-24 bg-[#0C1929] text-white border-t border-b border-slate-800 relative">
		<!-- Spotlights -->
		<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-900/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
		
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
			<!-- Section Header -->
			<div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-20">
				<span class="text-sm font-sans bg-primary-cyan/15 text-primary-cyan px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded uppercase font-bold tracking-wider inline-block mb-2">Milestones & History</span>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white font-display">Our Milestones & Corporate History</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-xl mx-auto">
					A history of our persistent dedication to high-precision hardware localization and advanced software integration since 2011.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Timeline Tree -->
			<div class="relative border-l-2 border-slate-800 ml-4 md:ml-32 space-y-16">
				
				<!-- Period 1 -->
				<div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12">
					<!-- Dot indicator -->
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-950 border-2 border-primary-cyan rounded-full shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(0,229,255,0.6)]"></div>
					<!-- Desktop floating year label -->
					<div class="absolute left-[-160px] top-0 hidden md:block w-32 text-right">
						<span class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-white">2021 - 2026</span>
						<p class="text-sm text-primary-cyan font-semibold">Leap Forward</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-cyan uppercase md:hidden block mb-2">2021 - 2026 · Leap Forward</span>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">Global Market Deployment & Brand Expansion</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-300">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-primary-cyan font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2025.Pres</span>
								<span>Released the overhauled 19-inch Rack-type industrial system <strong class="text-white">DSPAUT R5</strong> and high-performance PAUT/UT portable instruments <strong class="text-white">T3 / B3</strong>.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-primary-cyan font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2024</span>
								<span>Established domestic and international B2B NDT supply chains with contracts in Vietnam, Brunei, Cambodia, and major industry partners (KPIENG, InnoDis, Azutek, SM, etc.).</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-primary-cyan font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2023</span>
								<span>Expanded overseas exports to Dubai, UAE, Uzbekistan, and Mexico, successfully completing heavy-industry field verification and B2B contracts.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-primary-cyan font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2022</span>
								<span>Developed and launched the cost-efficient portable PAUT instrument <strong class="text-white">DSPAUT B1</strong>.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-primary-cyan font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2021</span>
								<span>Re-engineered the physical housing and updated the integrated software suite for the flagship <strong class="text-white">DSPAUT P5</strong>.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Period 2 -->
				<div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12">
					<!-- Dot indicator -->
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-500 rounded-full"></div>
					<!-- Desktop floating year label -->
					<div class="absolute left-[-160px] top-0 hidden md:block w-32 text-right">
						<span class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-400">2016 - 2020</span>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-semibold">Industrial Evolution</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase md:hidden block mb-2">2016 - 2020 · Growth Era</span>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white/90 mb-4">NDT Proprietary Hardwares & IP Patent Registration</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-400">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-300 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2020</span>
								<span>Developed the 64CH:128El multi-channel NDT system <strong class="text-white">S3+</strong> and the 19-inch Rack-type industrial system <strong class="text-white">R3</strong>.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-300 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2019</span>
								<span>Developed the ultra-compact portable NDT model <strong class="text-white">DSPAUT P1</strong>. Conducted clinical blood flow monitoring projects with Seoul St. Mary's Hospital (2019~2024).</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-300 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2018</span>
								<span>Developed and launched South Korea's first fully proprietary portable PAUT NDT instrument, <strong class="text-white">DSPAUT P5</strong>.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-300 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2017</span>
								<span>Successfully developed the domestic multi-port system PAUT <strong class="text-white">S3</strong> and co-designed Alpinion Medical Systems' HIFU RFG hardware.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-300 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2016</span>
								<span>Created South Korea's first industrial PAUT hardware prototype (<strong class="text-white">M3</strong>). Secured ISO 9001/14001 certification and passed 4 categories of the rigorous US **EPRI Performance Demonstration (EPRI PD)** nuclear testing validation standards.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Period 3 -->
				<div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-12">
					<!-- Dot indicator -->
					<div class="absolute -left-[9px] top-1.5 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 border-2 border-slate-700 rounded-full"></div>
					<!-- Desktop floating year label -->
					<div class="absolute left-[-160px] top-0 hidden md:block w-32 text-right">
						<span class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-600">2011 - 2015</span>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-semibold">Foundation</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="bg-slate-900/20 border border-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase md:hidden block mb-2">2011 - 2015 · Foundation</span>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white/70 mb-4">Incorporation & Medical Diagnostic Technology Collaborations</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-500">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2013~2015</span>
								<span>Co-engineered and developed Alpinion Medical Systems' Handheld HCU-type diagnostic unit, E-Cube i7 and HW schematic architectures.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2011~2012</span>
								<span>Co-engineered and developed Alpinion Medical Systems' high-resolution clinical cart scanner E-Cube 7 core modules.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span class="text-slate-500 font-semibold w-24 shrink-0 font-sans">2011.08</span>
								<span>Incorporated <strong class="text-slate-450">SEONGSANLAB Co., Ltd.</strong> and officially opened our corporate research facility.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Awards & Certifications Section -->
	<section id="certifications" class="py-24 bg-slate-950 text-white border-b border-slate-800 relative scroll-mt-24">
		<!-- Spotlight overlay -->
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-blue-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
		
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
			<!-- Section Header -->
			<div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16">
				<span class="text-sm font-sans bg-primary-cyan/15 text-primary-cyan px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded uppercase font-bold tracking-wider inline-block mb-2">Awards & Certifications</span>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white font-display">Official Credentials & IP Achievements</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-xl mx-auto">
					Verified technical credentials and international standards passed by SEONGSANLAB.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Certifications Grid -->
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				
				<!-- Item 1: National R&D Project Performance -->
				<div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-primary-cyan/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,229,255,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div>
						<!-- Dynamic Visual Badge -->
						<div class="relative w-full h-44 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/80 overflow-hidden mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-primary-cyan/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(#00E5FF_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:12px_12px]"></div>
							<div class="absolute w-24 h-24 bg-primary-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-xl animate-pulse"></div>
							<!-- Blueprint & Radar/Circuit Design -->
							<svg class="w-28 h-28 text-primary-cyan/20 group-hover:text-primary-cyan/40 transition-colors duration-500" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" />
								<path d="M50 5 V95 M5 50 H95" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 2" />
								<!-- Circuit Lines -->
								<path d="M25 25 L35 35 H65 L75 25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" />
								<path d="M25 75 L35 65 H65 L75 75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" />
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="6" fill="#00E5FF" class="animate-ping opacity-25" />
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="4" fill="#00E5FF" />
								<circle cx="35" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3B82F6" />
								<circle cx="65" cy="35" r="2.5" fill="#3B82F6" />
								<circle cx="35" cy="65" r="2.5" fill="#3B82F6" />
								<circle cx="65" cy="65" r="2.5" fill="#3B82F6" />
							</svg>
							<!-- High-Tech Seal tag -->
							<div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-800 rounded-md px-2 py-0.5 flex items-center space-x-1 shadow-md">
								<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-primary-cyan rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
								<span class="text-[10px] font-sans font-bold tracking-wider text-slate-300">R&D INNOVATION</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
							<span class="text-2xl">🔬</span>
							<h4 class="text-base font-bold text-white group-hover:text-primary-cyan transition-colors">National R&D Project Performance</h4>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
							Successfully participated in and executed high-profile national R&D projects funded by the Ministry of SMEs and Startups, Seoul Business Agency, and the Korea Medical Device Development Fund, securing pioneering ultrasound NDT and real-time blood-flow monitoring capabilities.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 2: EPRI Performance Demonstration -->
				<div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-blue-400/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(59,130,246,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div>
						<!-- Dynamic Visual Badge -->
						<div class="relative w-full h-44 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/80 overflow-hidden mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-blue-400/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-950/20 via-transparent to-slate-950"></div>
							<div class="absolute w-24 h-24 bg-blue-600/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
							<!-- Nuclear Orbit Gauge -->
							<svg class="w-28 h-28 text-blue-500/20 group-hover:text-blue-400/40 transition-colors duration-500" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="38" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" />
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="34" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="6 3" class="animate-[spin_60s_linear_infinite]" />
								<!-- Orbits -->
								<ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="30" ry="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(30 50 50)" />
								<ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="30" ry="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(-30 50 50)" />
								<ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="30" ry="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(90 50 50)" />
								<circle cx="50" cy="50" r="4" fill="#3B82F6" />
							</svg>
							<!-- Validation Tag -->
							<div class="absolute inset-x-3 bottom-3 flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-800 rounded-md p-1.5 shadow-md">
								<span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-400 font-sans">NUCLEAR VALVE SPEC</span>
								<span class="text-[10px] bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold font-sans inline-block mb-2">EPRI PASSED</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
							<span class="text-2xl">⚛️</span>
							<h4 class="text-base font-bold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">EPRI PD Validation Passed</h4>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
							Passed 4 major nuclear-grade testing validations under the US Electric Power Research Institute (EPRI) Performance Demonstration criteria:<br/>
							<span class="block mt-2 font-sans text-xs text-slate-400 space-y-0.5">
								• 2016.03: EPRI PD - Pipe<br/>
								• 2016.05: EPRI PD - Shell<br/>
								• 2016.07: EPRI PD - SI Nozzle<br/>
								• 2016.08: EPRI PD - Nozzle
							</span>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 3: ISO Certifications -->
				<div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-amber-500/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(245,158,11,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div>
						<!-- Dynamic Visual Badge -->
						<div class="relative w-full h-44 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/80 overflow-hidden mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-amber-400/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-950/10 via-transparent to-slate-950"></div>
							<div class="absolute w-24 h-24 bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
							<!-- ISO Badge Shield -->
							<svg class="w-26 h-26 text-amber-500/20 group-hover:text-amber-400/40 transition-colors duration-500" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<path d="M50 12 L82 22 V52 C82 70 68 85 50 90 C32 85 18 70 18 52 V22 L50 12 Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" />
								<path d="M50 18 L76 26 V49 C76 64 65 77 50 82 C35 77 24 64 24 49 V26 L50 18 Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-dasharray="3 3" />
								<text x="50" y="44" fill="currentColor" font-family="monospace" font-size="7" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle">ISO 9001</text>
								<text x="50" y="56" fill="currentColor" font-family="monospace" font-size="7" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle">ISO 14001</text>
								<circle cx="50" cy="70" r="3" fill="currentColor" class="opacity-30" />
							</svg>
							<div class="absolute bottom-3 right-3 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-md px-2 py-0.5">
								<span class="text-[10px] font-sans font-bold text-amber-400">QMS / EMS CERTIFIED</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-4">
							<span class="text-2xl">⚙️</span>
							<h4 class="text-base font-bold text-white group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">ISO 9001 / 14001 Credentials</h4>
						</div>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
							Attained official ISO 9001 Quality Management and ISO 14001 Environmental Management certifications (May 2016). Ensures international standards of production and QA.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Item 4: Hardware KC & CE Certification -->
				<div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-purple-400/50 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(168,85,247,0.15)] transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between">
					<div>
						<!-- Dynamic Visual Badge -->
						<div class="relative w-full h-44 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl border border-slate-800/80 overflow-hidden mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-purple-400/30 transition-all duration-300">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] bg-[radial-gradient(#C084FC_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:16px_16px]"></div>
							<!-- Electromagnetic Wave Visual Vector -->
							<svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-purple-900/20" viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<path d="M 0 60 Q 30 40, 60 60 T 120 60" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" />
								<path d="M 0 60 Q 30 80, 60 60 T 120 60" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" />
							</svg>
							<!-- KC and CE marks in layout -->
							<div class="relative z-10 flex items-center space-x-6 text-slate-400">
								<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
									<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-primary-cyan/80 group-hover:text-primary-cyan transition-colors duration-300" viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="currentColor">
										<path d="M 12 10 L 12 40 L 22 40 L 22 28 L 38 40 L 38 28 L 22 10 Z" />
										<circle cx="38" cy="16" r="4" />
									</svg>
									<span class="text-[10px] font-sans mt-1 text-slate-550">KC MARK</span>
								</div>
								<div class="w-px h-8 bg-slate-800"></div>
								<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
									<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400/80 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300" viewBox="0 0 50 50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.5">
